Titolo: Guardian's Crusade

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Guardian's Crusade, known in Japan as Knight & Baby (ナイト&ベイビー, Naito ando Beibī), is a role-playing video game developed by Tamsoft and released for the PlayStation in 1998. The gameplay is that of a standard turn based role playing game with non-random encounters. While intended for an adult audience as well, the game was something of an introduction to RPGs for children. The game did not enjoy commercial success.

Genere: Role-playing video game

Valutazione: N/A
